node.text: “I use singing bowls to promote relaxation until I get into a deep state of meditation. When I circle the bowls with my mallet, they create healing vibrations known as sound therapy—an ancient Tibetan tradition.” —@indira, who you can thank for this moment of peace in your feed. #everydaymadewell
